#1119<br>
The historic Southern Stove Lofts community is located at the north-east corner of Hermitage Road and Leigh Street, in Richmond. Located just blocks from the Fan, we offer a state of the art apartment community accommodated with luxury amenities. Our apartment homes range in size from 520 square feet (1 bedroom) to 1,200 square feet (3 bedrooms) with many different layouts available. Some of the unique details included in our beautiful apartment homes are imported granite counter tops, industrial stained concrete, Eco-friendly bamboo wood floors, full size stack-able washer and dryer in every apartment, and stainless steel appliances.<br>
<br>
Property Amenities:<br>
<br>
- Salt Water Pool<br>
- Package Receiving<br>
- On-site Management<br>
- Storage Space<br>
